3.7 Export Compliance
You are responsible for compliance with U.S. and international export laws and regulations that may apply to your use and distribution of the software and any data, models, or hardware you control with it.

3.8 Privacy and Telemetry
This project does not intentionally collect personal data or transmit telemetry on its own. If you enable telemetry features in your editor or platform, their respective privacy policies apply. Scripts you author may send data to services you choose; you are responsible for informing users and meeting applicable privacy obligations.

